the beautifully maintained stadiums  is
Stadium Management South Africa (SMSA).SMSA has managed to win well over 20 international awards in
the past two years and they have also been recognised as a top empowerment
company in Mzansi."We employ people of all races, we make sure that we
acknowledge women and internationally you find few women working in the stadium
