Orlando stadium for the City of Johannesburg.Stadium Management over the years has committed to providing
opportunities and making a positive impact on the lives of its surrounding
communities.SMSA formed the Stadium Management Trust in order to provide
an opportunity to the underprivileged and previously disadvantaged members in
its communities.The Trust has provided job opportunities, feeding schemes,
stadium tours, complimentary tickets and internships to the local communities.